        "norm": "cosmopolitan enough that a bird-folk merchant draws no more notice than any other commuter, the city organises its inter-district movement with a firm hand — private vehicles are confined to designated transit corridors or must yield to the public transit network within city limits, the prohibition on unrestricted sliding being less a courtesy than a security doctrine."
